# Terraform working directory and state (any week)
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Saved binary plans. The JSON evidence under each week's evidence/ is committed on purpose.
**/tfplan
**/*.tfplan

# Local variable values (environment-specific; may hold sensitive data)
**/terraform.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars.json

# Editor / backup artifacts
*.orig
*.bak

# Kept intentionally (do NOT ignore):
#   **/.terraform.lock.hcl  -> pins provider versions
#   **/evidence/plan.json   -> machine-readable compliance evidence
